      "instruction": "<p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Tear your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> to a medium bowl with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>curry powder</strong> (save the rest for later!), a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and stir to combine – this is your <strong>crouton marinade</strong></p>",
