      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a chopping board and cover with some <strong>cling film</strong></p><p>Bash the<strong> chicken </strong>with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until evenly flattened – this is your<strong> chicken escalope</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1693291415002-x200.jpg",
