            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your<strong> breaded chicken</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a drizzle more oil if your pan is looking a little dry!</p><p>Drain the <strong>quick-pickled chilli</strong>,<strong> </strong>add the <strong>pickling liquid</strong> to the katsu dressing and stir it all together</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
